chile , china to establish peke copper plant the chilean state copper corpor , codelco , the privately-own chilean copper fabric madeco and chine interest are to establish a copper tube plant in peke , codelco 's u.k. subsidiari chile copper ltd said . the plant is design to produc 5,000 tonn in the first five year and 8,000 tonn as from year six . total invest is estim at 10 mln dlr , of which the chilean will contribut two mln . codelco and madeco have form the chilean wrought copper compani to take a 50 pct stake in a new compani call peke santiago tube compani with the chine hold the other half .